<subSubSection id="E308825B95DD84D50E265A206F608FA1" lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="71" pageId="1" pageNumber="70" type="paratypes">
<paragraph id="DCA3E943C0ED94AC085952DFB4E680C6" pageId="1" pageNumber="70">Paratypes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1523040AFED601D7566F8582DD7F0F14" lastPageId="2" lastPageNumber="71" pageId="1" pageNumber="70">
1 female, Nanling, Shaoguan, Guangdong, China, 21.IX.2006, Min Wang leg.; 3 males, Nanling, Shaoguan, Guangdong, China, 2.XII.2007, Liu-Sheng Chen leg.; 3 males, 3.XII.2008, Liu-Sheng Chen and Hou-Shuai Wang leg., Nanling, Shaoguan, Guangdong, China; 1 male, 10.XII.2009, Hou-Shuai Wang leg., Nanling, Shaoguan, Guangdong, China. Deposited in the Department of Entomology, South 
